<a href="/wiki/Homeland_Security_Advisory_System" title="Homeland Security Advisory System">Homeland Security Advisory System</a> chart in the <a href="/wiki/United_States" title="United States">United States</a>, which has been criticized as encouraging the public to fear terrorism.</div>
</div>
